Package ru.nsu.fit.lylova

Class DataBaseListener

java.lang.Object
ru.nsu.fit.lylova.DataBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener, DataListener
public class DataBaseListener extends Object implements DataListener
This class provides an empty implementation of DataListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
